@data.characters.f3_mother.name: What would you like to do? 

@data.characters.f3_son_4.name: Build a house out of bed sheets! 

@data.characters.f3_mother.name: Great idea! What do we need to do first?

@data.characters.f3_mother.name: Well done,
@data.characters.f3_son_4.name! This is a wonderful bedsheet house. 

@data.characters.f3_son_4.name: Can we read our bedtime story here tonight?
